		<bioghist encodinganalog="545">
			<head>Biographical History</head>
			<p>American author, fantasy and science fiction short story writer and novelist.</p>
		</bioghist>
		
		<scopecontent encodinganalog="520">
			<head>Scope and Contents of the Collection</head>
			<p>The Anne McCaffrey Papers, 1947-1967, consist of correspondence, memorabilia and writings.  Correspondence includes an undated letter and memorandum.  Memorabilia consists of one unidentified photograph.</p><p>Writings, 1947-1967, form the bulk of the collection and are divided into four groups: books, honors thesis, plays, and short stories.  Within these groups, arrangement is alphabetical by title.</p>
		</scopecontent>
		
		<arrangement encodinganalog="351$a">
			<head>Arrangement of the Collection</head>
			<p>Material is arranged alphabetically by type and within that alphabetically by title.</p>
		</arrangement>
		
